## ⚙️ Vercel SPA Routing Fix

**File:** `vercel.json` (project root)

```json
{
  "rewrites": [
    { "source": "/(.*)", "destination": "/index.html" }
  ]
}
```

> This is required for React Router to work on Vercel. Without it, direct URL access (e.g., `avani-loan-services.vercel.app/contact`) returns 404. **Do NOT delete this file.**

